  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/UnderdogNBA/status/2034706891129999593",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, Embiid's injury history is a concern. Hope he's okay.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:20:44.818802+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/WeAreCavsNation/status/2034713346566418523",
      "reply_text": "That's a steep ask. One Finals appearance isn't a guarantee of a max extension.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:21:32.050654+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/CurryHicksSage/status/2034720555773931887",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, it's a big deal for them. High Point's been improving.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:22:28.055960+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BetMGMNews/status/2034717795188187137",
      "reply_text": "Milwaukee Bucks are getting a lot of love to cover. That's no surprise given their recent form.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:23:16.789008+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/bhallwfmy/status/2034720578016272592",
      "reply_text": "Big win for Coach Clayman and the Panthers. That game-winner will be remembered.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:23:54.895989+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ESPN_Schick/status/2034720085416280569",
      "reply_text": "That's dedication. Team-first attitude pays off.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:24:32.902894+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/followAdamA/status/2034713930816450624",
      "reply_text": "Defense matters, especially on the road. They need to tighten up in crunch time.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:25:23.436646+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/MotorCityBanter/status/2034714189533475002",
      "reply_text": "That's a big boost for the Pistons. Hope it's not too little, too late.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:26:11.344859+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/RussNeverLeft/status/2034706908934701562",
      "reply_text": "PPG doesn't equal MVP. Defense matters.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:26:48.815139+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/entchris723/status/2034683278213750888",
      "reply_text": "Prime Curry's shooting is insane, but Payton's D is elite. Can't choose between those two.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:27:29.403967+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Dashytwo/status/2034713957110329774",
      "reply_text": "That was a highlight reel game from him",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:38:26.468806+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FOS/status/2034724841433993296",
      "reply_text": "That's a cool story. Shows how much respect Steph and Seth have for their dad.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:39:04.963402+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PistonsThoughts/status/2034724210787119126",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, that's the only way it makes sense for Detroit. Need that secondary creator",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T20:39:38.776498+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BoogieFlandMuse/status/2034728947229852160",
      "reply_text": "Movement points per 75 is a great metric for pace. Wonder what it says about their offense.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:00:38.511491+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/CollegeHoopsTIk/status/2034727597838311905",
      "reply_text": "Fast breaks can be huge. But let's see if they can sustain it.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:01:15.190228+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/OdellBretthamJr/status/2034734776586740109",
      "reply_text": "Not sure I agree with that. LeBron's NCAA tourney resume is still impressive.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:10:41.462599+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Dee_rose901/status/2034725718337188310",
      "reply_text": "Impressive consistency against the Lakers",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:11:17.302579+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Checkmatee27/status/2034735358261567837",
      "reply_text": "Still crazy how he took down LeBron in the Finals. That series was intense",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:11:58.192152+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/SInow/status/2034729159390359876",
      "reply_text": "Seven straight is huge, but let's see them without AD for a game",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:12:36.875105+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/zeketrontay/status/2034718479840944515",
      "reply_text": "Load management has been a topic of debate. Some teams prioritize player safety, others see it as a strategy.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-19T21:13:29.903784+00:00"
    }
